&lt;li&gt;Aggregating user feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a team-oriented group that collaborates closely with each other and our cross-functional stakeholders. Together, we identify opportunities to design and scale repeatable processes, and we bring clarity and insight to address ambiguous and complex problems at the intersection of go-to-market and product.&lt;/p&gt;
