&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead strategic finance support for the Global Product Sales organization support Payments + Link Sales CRO OR MaaS CRO and Alliances and Channels, driving insight into user-level performance, sales performance, pipeline conversion, quota attainment, and strategic account planning - contributing to recurring business performance reporting cadences.&lt;/li&gt;
