&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Sales, Sales Operations &amp;amp; Strategy, and Marketing to assess ROI of Product Sales investment decisions, GTM initiatives and customer acquisition strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refine, scale, and where necessary implement robust reporting and dashboards that track the right KPIs including our funnel and key investment drivers. Assess product attach motion for front door and cross-sell products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and drive opportunities for process automation and data streamlining to improve reporting accuracy and decision velocity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a key contributor to quarterly business reviews and long-range planning exercises, providing strategic recommendations and scenario analyses for Product Sales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex financial and sales data into clear narratives for executive audiences in both GTM and Product Leadership forums.&lt;/li&gt;
